title: New Kids On The Block - Summertime (Single).m122
description: New kids on the Block and their new video for "Summertime". The song is fantastic, summer-smash and it should be appreciated in the charts too. But who ever said the backstreet boys are old, haven&#039;t seen these fellows! Enough for that, the video was cool. Very predictable though. I knew what kind of video they would do to this as soon as I heard the track. They look so much younger in the video too. Anyway, Great song and the video fits to it!
